 {"id":"wa-3g47","title":"FTUI-02.1.a Define Cargo feature matrix and compile combinations","description":"## Background
Migration requires explicit compile-mode guarantees so unsupported or drifting feature combinations fail early.

## Deliverables
- canonical feature matrix (legacy-only, hybrid, ftui-only, test modes)
- compile-check plan for each supported combination
- policy for disallowed combinations and expected failure messages

## Acceptance Criteria
